Doc. to access the API(in Local Machine):

Step-1) Run the project in the local machine .
Step-2) Then from JMeter hit the API(with PUT request) as : http://localhost:8080/glaucus/increment/number
Step-3) The process or architecture will follow as :

Client(Browser) --> Dispatcher Servlet(Spring-Servlet.xml) --> Controller --> Service --> DAO 

(The description for each classes is given in the respective classes)
